</ul>
<p><a name="Detention_and_torture_centers" id="Detention_and_torture_centers"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Condor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Detention and torture centers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Detention and torture centers</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Colonia_Dignidad" title="Colonia Dignidad" class="mw-redirect">Colonia Dignidad</a>, a bizarre and secretive German enclave in activity until 2005, put under state administration end of 2005</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Esmeralda_(BE-43)" title="Esmeralda (BE-43)">Esmeralda (BE-43)</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Estadio_Nacional_de_Chile" title="Estadio Nacional de Chile">Estadio Nacional de Chile</a></li>
